{"tid":1378121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果政府機關牽頭發動全港罷工，罷定唔罷？！","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:05.000Z","uid":49774,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0067b3e95ba6f74b8a5092911bd6fe62be6dbb","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"有公務員組織聯絡緊之前有份聯署既所有政府部門<br />\n包括紀律部隊 準備以媒體發佈罷工安排<br />\n<br />\n佢地都講得好清楚罷工原因<br />\n主要原因係唔想因為政警既欺壓手段影響到公共工作<br />\n同埋服務市民既初心 <br />\n並非完全同五大訴求有關 但都歡迎持不同訴求既市民加入罷工<br />\n<br />\n但目前收到消防聯署人就住罷工行動回覆 <br />\n因為假若罷工潮開始 佢地要準備做保護市民既backup 所以未必響應運動<br />\n但其它紀律部隊同政府部門包括海關 入境 <br />\n就話聯絡緊之前有參與聯署既同事再決定是否響應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnyway 一句講哂<br />\n<br />\n罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51e221ca1122ee1ee85017839779324e1e888f5","tid":1378121,"uid":263792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"1c45a8a88461ac260efb48012d620bd5b1d0585f","tid":1378121,"uid":166982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"3cbd473a4303f7e5765ff1b836e47bbd3d09d60d","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"順帶一提 暫時講到明響應既公務員有接近二千人 如果身邊有公務員朋友既 而佢又未同發起組織接觸過既話 麻煩都可以通知一聲"},{"pid":"a38491357aa350fb336451b43e0756f811597274","tid":1378121,"uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e98ec984e7f1f5cce8b883ea11d10695cbdeac","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897f120fc38abcf674f279891e2f4e7d452737f8","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"推到全世界都響應"},{"pid":"f9da4a79e99efc475737cf84c803a58cc69e8d59","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c168fcf5d5ed57b0ace60fee29120570314acaeb","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3fa84e72cf29fec65b843620acb476e5e47755ce","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"0834bc0a9d5b99ec00f446b74b03e58c976e9436","tid":1378121,"uid":202316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"6f833d4c58356a8b5d9e997f471116272978958d","tid":1378121,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"罷，黑警搞到其他前線公務員都比市民屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔罷對唔住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5320d7e5ccee0cc55aeebbceb9cb81dc1523a33","tid":1378121,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救香港<br />\n請罷工</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手停口停<br />\n守護我城</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b22197c1471461928a0218d4fb7601dbe15a3c2d","tid":1378121,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45084ee313fe75b6c3e429bcd8e3130388a7494c","tid":1378121,"uid":49774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}